Cook,<br><br>
RUNNING battle? Us mortarmen couldn't run even if we tried. Ever try humpin' an 81? 'Course you jar heads had them itty bitty 60's.<br><br>
Us mortar guys liked to lay back and let the rifle platoons do the runnin' (forward, of course)! We had important things to do like choose up sides for Spades or divide up the C Rations. Now you know why you never got the pound cake and peaches!<br><br>
Thanks for the nice story. 
